{"tid":1397184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於旺角，大家入嚟睇睇，特別係前缐","createTime":"2019-08-02T11:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:56:54.000Z","uid":185213,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b022a57be41ead68670d871895e2a25f28cc5990","tid":1397184,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"未fact check, 較少開po, 大家自己判斷，特別係前線手足<br />\n有朋友send 比我，話啲狗放左啲野係旺角，會煽動你地用，大家當草船借箭又好，啲狗引人犯法拉人又好，希望大家睇睇。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係比前線決定</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHBbquL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHBbquL.png&h=33fc560e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEx9WBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEx9WBr.png&h=4a7abb1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mh4z7H7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMh4z7H7.png&h=e15f5769&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01394f71de7967ade09571f841e5444f436c53af","tid":1397184,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"推一推，等更多手足知道，自己決定"},{"pid":"37bf617535f2e51809f5d1b324de553a6f9f2ff8","tid":1397184,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:03:08.000Z","msg":"推一推，等更多手足知道，自己決定"},{"pid":"0da928d3321b2fad864045f56c3a01ee4a47ce12","tid":1397184,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"推一推，等更多手足知道，自己決定"},{"pid":"74ba8e351d3bde98f93d2814666c77bb143880c6","tid":1397184,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"推一推，等更多手足知道，自己決定"},{"pid":"a5f4e7a705e2ebea6bd035f29a836f8eb47dc148","tid":1397184,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\